BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Uranus conjunction Mercury
DESCRIPTION:Transit Uranus (Pisces 28°55’) - conjunction - Natal Mercury \nYou will have many unexpected ideas that will come as lightning in a clear sky. Your intuition will play an important role in your life and your daily routine will become much more interesting. Beware of the tendency to get nervous or to make unexpected conclusions. You may also say something you will regret later. It is not a good time to travel.  \n \nTransit Uranus in Natal 6th house: \nUranus will bring unexpected changes to your daily routine and schedule. The reason for these changes is your subconscious desire to break free from routine and your desire not to be one of the crowd. If you resist changing your rituals, you may be forced to do so by external influences. Your work life may experience shocks in the form of flexible working hours or frequent job changes. You may also start working as a freelancer, get an unusual job or work in an unusual work environment. You will need a job that gives you enough freedom, otherwise you may lose motivation. Your attitudes toward health may change, you may for example have a newly found interest in alternative medicine. Yoga and other activities that involve mind and body will be beneficial to you.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20110220T072800Z
DTEND:20110220T072800Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165913Z
UID:1_tr_ur_co_me
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Neptune conjunction Venus
DESCRIPTION:Transit Neptune (Pisces 4°24’) - conjunction - Natal Venus \nYou will be very sensitive and vulnerable. You will also be very receptive to the needs of others and you will be able to understand them more. However, you will have difficulties perceiving the true self of the people you love. You will also be impractical in money matters, so it is better not to make serious financial decisions or purchases in this period. \n \nTransit Neptune in Natal 5th house: \nDuring this transit you will long for romance and dating, but there is a risk of disillusionment with the people toward whom this interest is directed. You are not able to see people as they really are because you are wearing rose-coloured glasses. You may be giving your love to someone who does not deserve it. You are willing to sacrifice yourself, even if you do not get anything back. The advantage of this transit is that it brings creative enthusiasm and activates your imagination and you can discover new interests and hobbies.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20130407T101400Z
DTEND:20130407T101400Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165913Z
UID:2_tr_ne_co_ve
END:VEVENT
