BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Pluto conjunction IC
DESCRIPTION:Transit Pluto (Capricorn 12°27’) - conjunction - Natal IC \n \n \nTransit Pluto in Natal 3rd house: \nYour daily routine and the way you live your life will become very important to you. This transit will start your profound psychological transformation based on self-criticism and doubts about yourself. Do not be afraid to change shallow thinking patterns that no longer serve you. You may often be in a bad mood and you will be obsessed with your interests. You will also have the need to be in control of your relationships with others. Carefully read any contracts or documents before signing them. If the Pluto transit is in this house of your horoscope in combination with difficult aspects, you may have a car accident or have an accident on a trip, so take extra caution. \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20140205T193900Z
DTEND:20140205T193900Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165913Z
UID:6_tr_pl_co_ic
END:VEVENT
