BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Uranus conjunction DSC
DESCRIPTION:Transit Uranus (Aries 10°48’) - conjunction - Natal DSC \n \n \nTransit Uranus in Natal 7th house: \nYou will experience many changes in your relationships with your loved ones during this transit. These changes may be triggered by unexpected events or by the personality of your loved ones, who may now be less reliable. The effect of this transit will be that you will need greater independence in your relationships and that you will not tolerate well if your partner is too dependent on you. You may be attracted to unusual people. They will bring feelings of excitement and instability into your life. You may plunge into romantic relationships with enthusiasm and quickly fall in love, but you may fall out of love just as quickly. If you are in a relationship that is stagnant, it will be difficult for you to remain in it.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20140303T094000Z
DTEND:20140303T094000Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165913Z
UID:8_tr_ur_co_ds
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Neptune conjunction Jupiter
DESCRIPTION:Transit Neptune (Pisces 7°26’) - conjunction - Natal Jupiter \nYour imagination will be at its peak and you will be attracted to the fantasy genre. You will also be much more creative. It is a good time to travel and study philosophy.  \n \nTransit Neptune in Natal 5th house: \nDuring this transit you will long for romance and dating, but there is a risk of disillusionment with the people toward whom this interest is directed. You are not able to see people as they really are because you are wearing rose-coloured glasses. You may be giving your love to someone who does not deserve it. You are willing to sacrifice yourself, even if you do not get anything back. The advantage of this transit is that it brings creative enthusiasm and activates your imagination and you can discover new interests and hobbies.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
