BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Uranus conjunction Sun
DESCRIPTION:Transit Uranus (Aries 20°41’) - conjunction - Natal Sun \nThis transit may awaken your ability to see the true meaning of your life. It is time you put yourself first, regardless of what others expect of you. As a result, you may resign at work or leave your marriage because it will no longer suit you.  \n \nTransit Uranus in Natal 7th house: \nYou will experience many changes in your relationships with your loved ones during this transit. These changes may be triggered by unexpected events or by the personality of your loved ones, who may now be less reliable. The effect of this transit will be that you will need greater independence in your relationships and that you will not tolerate well if your partner is too dependent on you. You may be attracted to unusual people. They will bring feelings of excitement and instability into your life. You may plunge into romantic relationships with enthusiasm and quickly fall in love, but you may fall out of love just as quickly. If you are in a relationship that is stagnant, it will be difficult for you to remain in it.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20160414T011600Z
DTEND:20160414T011600Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165913Z
UID:16_tr_ur_co_su
END:VEVENT
