BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Neptune conjunction Mercury
DESCRIPTION:Transit Neptune (Pisces 28°55’) - conjunction - Natal Mercury \nYou will be very creative and full of inspiration and imagination. However, you can easily get lost in it. This transit benefits artist and people who need communication and foreign languages at work. For other people this transit is not an easy period because it will bring them inability to concentrate, lack of motivation and the difficulty in understanding the people around them.  \n \nTransit Neptune in Natal 6th house: \nDuring this transit you will be much more prone to stress and psychosomatic health disorders. You will also be more prone to the negative effects of medicines. There may be confusions in your work life, or your work may lead you to charity activities. The influence of Neptune in the 6th house may cause disruptions in your daily routine. A good way to deal with the stress of these disruptions, is doing some spiritual practices, like yoga, meditation, etc. For some individuals, it might be a good period to deal with health issues via hypnosis - quit smoking, address some stress-related and other psychosomatic issues. \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20240430T162400Z
DTEND:20240430T162400Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165913Z
UID:19_tr_ne_co_me
END:VEVENT
