BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Neptune conjunction DSC
DESCRIPTION:Transit Neptune (Aries 10°48’) - conjunction - Natal DSC \n \n \nTransit Neptune in Natal 7th house: \nThis transit brings complications to partner relationships. The person you love may seem more distant, or you may be too demanding and expect too much. Their behaviour may be frustrating for you. Try to accept your partner for who he or she is and realize that you cannot control the other person; you should just love him or her unconditionally. If you’re single, you may be attracted to people who will hurt you. It is unlikely that you will meet the right person during this transit, so be careful if you meet a new romantic partner.  In business relationship be aware of misunderstandings, vagueness (in negotiations or contracts) or even deceit. \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20310119T135000Z
DTEND:20310119T135000Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165913Z
UID:26_tr_ne_co_ds
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Uranus conjunction Mars
DESCRIPTION:Transit Uranus (Gemini 24°26’) - conjunction - Natal Mars \nYou may feel impatient, but also full of energy. You will have the need to finish everything as quickly as possible. You will really enjoy physical activities and adventure sports such as paragliding and kayaking.   \n \nTransit Uranus in Natal 9th house: \nLook forward to unexpected experiences that will broaden your horizons. You will meet new and interesting people from all over the world and from different backgrounds. Your opinions and beliefs may change. You may also want to learn new things, but learning will be sporadic and inconsistent.  An opportunity to travel may arise rather unexpectedly and this journey can open your eyes in many ways.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20310708T145600Z
DTEND:20310708T145600Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165913Z
