BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Pluto conjunction Jupiter
DESCRIPTION:Transit Pluto (Pisces 7°26’) - conjunction - Natal Jupiter \nThis transit will give you enough optimism and the kind of thinking you need to achieve everything you want. But if you achieve success at the expense of other people, you will ultimately fail. If you do things with good intentions, the universe will reward you and you will overcome all the obstacles you encounter.  \n \nTransit Pluto in Natal 5th house: \nTransit Pluto in this house will bring aggressiveness or at least less tolerance into your love life. You might want to change your partner’s behaviour that bothers you and you may even use force. You will be more realistic. You should also expect more drama and a greater desire for relationships that will be much more intense and passionate. You may also have the tendency to play games and cause conflicts just to spice up your relationship. If you are single, it is possible that you will enter a relationship that will cause an intense transformation and change your life. If you have children, expect problems caused by their rebellious behaviour. Beware of your tendency towards manipulative behaviour and the tendency to control things around you.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
