BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Uranus conjunction Pluto
DESCRIPTION:Transit Uranus (Libra 5°03’) - conjunction - Natal Pluto \nPeople who were born in the mid-1960s have already experienced the effects of this transit. It causes revolutionary changes and confrontations as a result of suppressed ideas. The things in your life that you have coped badly with will now resurface and you will feel that you must change them. You should use this transit to get rid of things from the past that no longer serve you.  \n \nTransit Uranus in Natal 12th house: \nThis transit helps you to break free of the cycles and burdens you are not aware of and that cause obstacles on your way. Various events or coincidences may occur at the beginning of this process. There is a risk that your secrets or private information will be revealed. You will have the desire to help others selflessly and anonymously.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20521226T213400Z
DTEND:20521226T213400Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165913Z
