BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Uranus conjunction Ascendant
DESCRIPTION:Transit Uranus (Libra 10°48’) - conjunction - Natal Ascendant \n \n \nTransit Uranus in Natal 1st house: \nDuring this transit, you will have the need to get out of your comfort zone and express yourself freely. Uranus will bring big changes, and when it passes through the 1st house, these changes will be related to your personality and appearance. You will not be concerned with what others think and expect from you. You will have the need to be independent and you will be open to unconventional experiences. You will also be more willing to take risks and plunge into things without fear. Other people may be surprised by your fearless and rebellious attitude, so you may feel growing distance between you and some people. Beware of impulsive behaviour.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20550712T153600Z
DTEND:20550712T153600Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165913Z
UID:52_tr_ur_co_as
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Uranus conjunction Uranus
DESCRIPTION:Transit Uranus (Libra 25°58’) - conjunction - Natal Uranus \nThis transit occurs every 84 years and its influence depends on how old you are. If you are young, it causes instability of the family environment. Later in life, it brings a sense of restlessness and nervousness resulting from constant stream of unexpected events in your life. You will be withdrawn and focus more on your spirituality. You will get rid of everyday worries and get a new outlook on what is important and what is not.  \n \nTransit Uranus in Natal 1st house: \nDuring this transit, you will have the need to get out of your comfort zone and express yourself freely. Uranus will bring big changes, and when it passes through the 1st house, these changes will be related to your personality and appearance. You will not be concerned with what others think and expect from you. You will have the need to be independent and you will be open to unconventional experiences. You will also be more willing to take risks and plunge into things without fear. Other people may be surprised by your fearless and rebellious attitude, so you may feel growing distance between you and some people. Beware of impulsive behaviour.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
